Type of Feat: Class
Specifics: A warrior of darkness concocts a magic oil with which to coat his favorite weapon. When applied, the oil grants a new supernatural ability chosen from the list below and it lasts 4 rounds per warrior of darkness level. This ability can be used ten times per day.

List of Choices:
Flaming (1d6 Fire)
Frost (1d6 Cold)
Vampiric (+2)
Shock (1d6 Electricity)
Massive Criticals (2d10)
Use: Automatic.